<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/20/gallery/ComfyUI_00446_.png" data-size="1224x1688"><img loading="lazy" src="https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/20/gallery/ComfyUI_00446_-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="768" height="1059"></a></figure>
