</div></div>
<p>I worked at a gas station and the owner did not mind if I drew while at work so long as all my duties were done by the end of my shift. I don't recall what my inspiration was for this one other then recalling where I created it which was as a clerk inside a gas station store. I was interested to see how AI would fill the scene and following my instructions to make the sketch a finished artwork.</p>
