<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00151_.png" data-size="1024x1024"><img loading="lazy" src="https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00151_-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="768" height="768"></a></figure>
</div></div>
<p>The concept for this logo was to create the energy and feel of big and showing a bang and the typical bomb explosion cloud around a microphone I feel sells the idea, while relating to the mental visual picture created by this combination of words and imagery. This logo I used to test a few styles changes to see how AI handles this kind of imagery. Then I used AI to apply the logo concept to a mock-up location. I did not try to refine the logo with these images, I was more interested in AI ability to apply styles to words and imagery.</p>
            ]]>
        </content>
